We all know we should be eating more greens and protein and less carbs, sugar and fat\u2026 but then life happens. A busy schedule, cravings for unhealthy snacks or just the typical difficulties of adulting in general all contribute to the fact that we simply don\u2019t eat as well as we know we should.
